Project Title:
Task Management System Using Python Flask and MySQL

Problem Statement:
Many people find it difficult to remember and manage their daily tasks. They may forget important work, miss deadlines, or have trouble organizing their activities. A Task Management System helps users create, update, and track their tasks in one place, making it easier to stay organized and complete work on time.

Objective:
To develop a web-based Task Management System that helps users create, organize, track, and manage their daily tasks efficiently.

Backend:
Python 
Frontend:
